title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 17 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 17 2021
description:
Day two of Rittenhouse jury deliberations. Biden White House silent on BLM threats to the Rittenhouse jury. Which political party is the party of riots? House Republicans reveal whistleblower documents exposing FBI use of counterterrorism tactics against parents. Does this mean the FBI has a file on Clay? Andy McCarthy, of National Review and former Assistant United States Attorney for the Southern District of New York, weighs in on Rittenhouse and other leading legal stories of the day. OSHA drops Biden vaccine mandate. Fauci claims boosters will make covid end faster.
